&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grow whiteboard adoption and experience:&lt;/strong&gt; Continuously raise the bar on the Klaxoon product experience to make it a world-class visual collaboration tool, with strong focus on driving adoption among Wrike customers and identifying high-value vertical use cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enable AI-native R&amp;amp;D:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute to building the processes, tooling, and mindsets needed for the R&amp;amp;D organization to work AI-natively, identifying where agentic workflows can change how the team operates and scales output.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop the PM team:&lt;/strong&gt; Coach, mentor, and grow a team of Product Managers - helping them move from feature ownership to strategic product leadership while building a shared product culture across Wrike and Klaxoon.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
